caption: Pasta's is our favorite local restaurant.  The bar is cozy and we are beyond happy that indoor dining has reopened and we can again sit in our favorite bar. Love to sit facing the window on Main St. and watch passersby. Jose's Ribs are a delicious appetizer.  The best warm bread, too.
